{"tid":1004301,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩買左對鞋 發覺呢個世界都幾美好","createTime":"2019-02-01T10:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T18:06:24.000Z","uid":10214,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"284895127c956b609f2b4b76c37627bc2abefb55","tid":1004301,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"睇中左對ultra boost <br />\n拎落嚟睇價錢嗰陣嚇左一跳<br />\n個價錢平左好多<br />\n咁就問有冇碼<br />\n點知真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住有個中佬就埋嚟r我水吹<br />\n話佢又睇中<br />\n跟住一齊試鞋一齊埋單<br />\n兩對仲有9折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n埋完單佢比返cash我<br />\n我仲問返佢要唔要單<br />\n臨出門口嗰陣仲祝佢新年快樂🎉<br />\n成個過程好流暢<br />\n<br />\n為美好的世界獻上祝福～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3gc4TK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3gc4TK.png&h=6528dcf0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5ebddb5139c98e703122a9e268e9c8734b8107a","tid":1004301,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36b30d76a668b94c9615b8e258e694d011a9a811","tid":1004301,"uid":149383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"個中佬終於賣左對假鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 世界真美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a5ea299defafb8a32c2c2e7f16db9d5091ccfd","tid":1004301,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b30d76a668b94c9615b8e258e694d011a9a811","tid":1004301,"uid":149383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"個中佬終於賣左對假鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 世界真美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ang